     <div type="dedication">
   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>Briefly to you that will Read.</head>
   <l>NOT vnto euery one can Reade, I write;</l>
   <l>But onely vnto those that can Reade right.</l>
   <l>And therefore if thou canst not Read it well,</l>
   <l>I pray thee lay it downe, and learne to spell.</l>
   <l>But if thou wilt be hewing, (like a drudge)</l>
   <l>Hewe on, and spare not, but forbeare to Iudge.</l>
   <byline>
      <hi>Thine if thou beest mine,</hi> Iohn Taylor.</byline>
</div>
